  <brief_title>Evaluation of NEXFIN During Cesarean Delivery to Detect Hypotension</brief_title>
  <acronym>NEXFIN-CESAR</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the System NEXFIN for Continuous and Non-invasive Measure of the Blood Pressure During Cesarean Delivery Practised Under Spinal Anesthesia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
